    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GO INSIDE AND RAVAGE THE DUNGEONS</h2>Jump into a rouge-like with semi-infinite dungeons, fast action gameplay, and items with unique effects.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HIGH RISK</h2>Dont forget, you only have one life.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242890/extras/8833d08305192df3b7ea593d6f7909b3.poster.avif?t=1771536389\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242890/extras/8833d08305192df3b7ea593d6f7909b3.webm?t=1771536389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242890/extras/8833d08305192df3b7ea593d6f7909b3.mp4?t=1771536389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FILLED WITH REPLAYABLE CONTENT</h2>Crawl into this randomly generated world with semi-infinite possabilities. <br>Each time getting and combining different weapons and relics for unique advantages.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MUCH TO DISCOVER</h2>Hoards of unique monsters with speciel abilities are guarding the dungeons from you. <br>Use and combine a ton of diffrent relics and weapons to get stronger and cut through them and their bosses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242890/extras/d5168c6815a2e23fc2b7765aa742693c.poster.avif?t=1771536389\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242890/extras/d5168c6815a2e23fc2b7765aa742693c.webm?t=1771536389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242890/extras/d5168c6815a2e23fc2b7765aa742693c.mp4?t=1771536389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
